===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fr|en}} {{term|république||republic|lang=fr}}, derived from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|rēs publica||republic|lang=la}}, from {{term|rēs||thing|lang=la}} + {{term|publicus|pūblica|public|lang=la}}; hence literally “the public thing”.

